::Hot Rod::

"Yeah, me too." He grabbed there glasses, and got refills. He sat back
down. He once again was right next to her. He wanted to be close to her.
"Here you go.", he said, putting the glass on the table. He finished off
his last energon cube. He wasn't sure what to say or do. So he just
kissed her, seeing what she would do.
